FEATURES
 * no buffer, but does pixel-by-pixel update
 * really slow
 * minimalistic
 * optimized for size
 * for small devices with minimal resources

LINKS
 * https://playground.arduino.cc/Main/SoftwareI2CLibrary
 * https://github.com/notisrac/TinyPrint

